.TH k2i-completions-power-shell 1  "k2i-completions-power-shell "
.SH NAME
k2i\-completions\-power\-shell \- Generate PowerShell completions
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBk2i\-completions\-power\-shell\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate PowerShell completions
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.SH EXTRA
EXAMPLE:
  k2i completions power\-shell > k2i.ps1
